{"tid":475701,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪充電之行","createTime":"2017-11-21T11:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T16:25:58.000Z","uid":39745,"like":9,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f5925953b6dc9309b75702fb8987e85d225fa39a","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:01:56.000Z","msg":"上次係獨遊東京<br />\n今次係同男友一齊去 7日6夜 <br />\n<br />\n題外話係今次Plan 純粹係因為男友生日<br />\n無諗過睇到少少紅葉<br />\n提提大家 記住睇天氣做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次係揀Hong Kong Express 中午1點飛<br />\n出發前一個月到不斷爆新聞 嚇到仆街<br />\n雖然今次無受影響 但之後永不錄用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDAY 1<br />\n11點機埸CHECK IN + 早餐<br />\n1點起飛<br />\n5點幾落機<br />\n8點前到難波區酒店<br />\n<br />\n今次住Dormy Inn飯店 - 難波高階天然溫泉<br />\n房細是常識，但廁所/沖涼/洗手分開晒真係唔鍾意。<br />\n<br />\nAGODA 理想圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://pix6.agoda.net/hotelImages/488/488305/488305_15081216320034135065.jpg?s=1024x768\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpix6.agoda.net%2FhotelImages%2F488%2F488305%2F488305_15081216320034135065.jpg%3Fs%3D1024x768&h=ffe77ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pix6.agoda.net/hotelImages/488/488305/488305_15081216320034135067.jpg?s=1024x768\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpix6.agoda.net%2FhotelImages%2F488%2F488305%2F488305_15081216320034135067.jpg%3Fs%3D1024x768&h=8b537811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pix6.agoda.net/hotelImages/488/488305/488305_17013108440050670927.jpg?s=1024x768\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpix6.agoda.net%2FhotelImages%2F488%2F488305%2F488305_17013108440050670927.jpg%3Fs%3D1024x768&h=88972a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pix6.agoda.net/hotelImages/488/488305/488305_14052908280019619461.jpg?s=1024x768\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpix6.agoda.net%2FhotelImages%2F488%2F488305%2F488305_14052908280019619461.jpg%3Fs%3D1024x768&h=f9aeb0ca&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先現實我BOOK個房型係無浴缸，仲要好柒。<br />\n其次酒店室內溫泉得30幾度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後個地點真係唔多好，係長堀橋同日本橋之間<br />\n行到返酒店要7-10分鐘 去難波站行大約15分鐘。<br />\n補充：隔音差<br />\n<br />\n不過張床好訓過APA，軟硬適中<br />\n另外包埋酒店自助早餐 有誠意幾好食。<br />\n<br />\n所以我俾6.5/10<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCHECK IN完去道頓堀食元祖元綠壽司<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f9ZEjpr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff9ZEjpr.jpg&h=c7b40a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/oSECxLz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FoSECxLz&h=1a4d0485&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n評語:不吃也可<br />\n大慨都叫做好過爭鮮，去日本可以唔洗食呢種壽司。<br />\n但每晚經過都有人排隊<br />\n<br />\n後來試咗四天皇對面間 章魚燒<br />\n唔記得咩名<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/U24XAYK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FU24XAYK.jpg&h=50a6660e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一早聽聞當地章魚燒唔啱香港人，果然覺得太淋身唔好食<br />\n一試就罷了。"},{"pid":"86ff4ce425ee247ac1247aa8fa04f377794a3d8d","tid":475701,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:07:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次係獨遊東京<br />\n今次係同男友一齊去 7日6夜 <br />\n<br />\n題外話係今次Plan 純粹係因為男友生日<br />\n無諗過睇到少少紅葉<br />\n提提大家 記住睇天氣做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次係揀Hong Kong Express 中午1點飛<br />\n出發前一個月到不斷爆新聞 嚇到仆街<br />\n雖然今次無受影響 但之後永不錄用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDAY 1<br />\n11點機埸CHECK IN + 早餐<br />\n1點起飛<br />\n5點幾落機<br />\n8點前到難波區酒店<br />\n<br />\n今次住Dormy Inn飯店 - 難波高階天然溫泉<br />\n房細是常識，但廁所/沖涼/洗手分開晒真係唔鍾意。<br />\n<br />\nAGODA 理想圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://pix6.agoda.net/hotelImages/488/488305/488305_15081216320034135065.jpg?s=1024x768\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpix6.agoda.net%2FhotelImages%2F488%2F488305%2F488305_15081216320034135065.jpg%3Fs%3D1024x768&h=ffe77ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pix6