re":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/193539_6320b43af2595ccd8d86a66f9fc074c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F193539_6320b43af2595ccd8d86a66f9fc074c2.jpg&h=b9a5eb40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fec3cc17aa1d94c6768e6d3077ce4fffd7c1dd1c","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"DAY2<br />\n大約9點出發奈良<br />\n1點幾去東大寺<br />\n4點幾返心齋橋食力太燒肉<br />\n6點幾食完行心齋橋<br />\n<br />\n由於車程耐，所以今日都算早出發。<br />\n<br />\n搭大約一個鐘車就到奈良<br />\n基本上一出站向右跟住行人方向就去到奈良公園<br />\n行左無耐就見到鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/193927_6f6a4e7cefb9371a4803d3e499b9a980.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F193927_6f6a4e7cefb9371a4803d3e499b9a980.JPG&h=377cad4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5487d5e4fab70629dd768a9f3e0245da664da548","tid":475701,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"兩條友去應該爽"},{"pid":"3685146eca21ff2699e00349b40556eadb98a134","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:44:48.000Z","msg":"鹿圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/194107_5b9635ce39d2b2cd9aa29a77f0f3e5d2.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F194107_5b9635ce39d2b2cd9aa29a77f0f3e5d2.JPG&h=efbdbff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/194204_805cc4de57987402dbee5104730f2d91.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F194204_805cc4de57987402dbee5104730f2d91.JPG&h=ceeb7b8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/194207_70a21b059c8ac72a9b93cec2548e62c4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F194207_70a21b059c8ac72a9b93cec2548e62c4.JPG&h=0ba40383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/194211_fdf885620d38803310a4db41e9b12520.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F194211_fdf885620d38803310a4db41e9b12520.JPG&h=36400449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/194213_9a45d5238981e4e0e56022d8a8623417.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F194213_9a45d5238981e4e0e56022d8a8623417.JPG&h=4d89f551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/194215_d511417bef87e29f83fff938169c8838.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F194215_d511417bef87e29f83fff938169c8838.JPG&h=5cf099d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係奈良公園嘅鹿都俾人餵飽晒<br />\n相反行到東大寺附近嘅鹿就好瘋狂<br />\n個男人買舊蕃薯食都俾鹿搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b1846399a423ebc172be1af832b419afb008f1","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩條友去應該爽</blockquote><br />\n增進感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實獨遊唔同爽法"},{"pid":"d5c198f585b9a779ab22403e7993daf9ba807eb0","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"續DAY 2 東大寺<br />\n<br />\n望住世界最大的木造建築，只係係到諗以前嘅人到底係幾辛苦先起到出嚟？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/195515_923c0c66fa2f8c6815a7d6b4472dbe76.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F195515_923c0c66fa2f8c6815a7d6b4472dbe76.JPG&h=22f6b95e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/195517_c9dc21530ac5caf5458fc3cfa3e3d963.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F195517_c9dc21530ac5caf5458fc3cfa3e3d963.JPG&h=6f2d582c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/195519_99a598d3cadc393111e2811ecaa52439.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F195519_99a598d3cadc393111e2811ecaa52439.JPG&h=e559291d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/195520_b374bddad71f82399657d15b5b3368e4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F195520_b374bddad71f82399657d15b5b3368e4.JPG&h=8534a91d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/195521_b596f2b612e67fa27143831aca815223.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F195521_b596f2b612e67fa27143831aca815223.JPG&h=7d7a762c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af089cf1a2a04742e4a7c20c641720e4711c1849","tid":475701,"uid":44814,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"食元祖元綠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f87ca04543a113c368cbcdabfec1f1ca2e58b96","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食元祖元綠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n恥笑我吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42579697cd8a79ab234df587b22eb0ac3b67253","tid":475701,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:04:29.000Z","msg":"我下個星期日去，睇下有冇野抄考下先"},{"pid":"23f6638d19e8eb95b6c373f7a1ae5904dd260a20","tid":475701,"uid":43819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:09:23.000Z","msg":"上次我住呢間間房好撚大 起馬可以放多2張單人床"},{"pid":"b9372c2f00a31d57ee5bb5d096fa4632e2a5bd0a","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:11:41.000Z","msg":"DAY 2<br />\n<br />\n去完奈良同東大寺都無咗大半日<br />\n後來去咗試連登仔都推介嘅力丸燒肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/200528_4f8a1e5e9da537e1aa4a7b82aa17f892.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F200528_4f8a1e5e9da537e1aa4a7b82aa17f892.JPG&h=d98e72c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n炭爐燒真係香好多<br />\n不過兩個人試唔到咁多肉<br />\n簡單講肉類、蔬菜、熟食、韓式野、炸物加埋甜品都幾抵玩。<br />\n可以一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/201053_77dbc1c0676ea8d99e1bca6922ab1d50.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F201053_77dbc1c0676ea8d99e1bca6922ab1d50.JPG&h=9c23efd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/201054_b0e52c7a61ee541ea1f1bf6f75575427.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F201054_b0e52c7a61ee541ea1f1bf6f75575427.JPG&h=2d1469b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/201131_f5efe695468ae852046f5ee28640710f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F201131_f5efe695468ae852046f5ee28640710f.JPG&h=f33e34b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb7ff903ef76905710cc3a0659d48fb4f42fc6f2","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我下個星期日去，睇下有冇野抄考下先</blockquote><br />\n隨便，我都係係連登參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9784709bbcfb201ce51af77c26e265034cec65d6","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:14:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次我住呢間間房好撚大 起馬可以放多2張單人床</blockquote><br />\n我BOOK個間是18平方公尺 一張大床<br />\n差少少開唔到行李"},{"pid":"1f08a67678ffd618817963d4f970aabd7d3f7bff","tid":475701,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我下個星期日去，睇下有冇野抄考下先</blockquote><br />\n隨便，我都係係連登參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登推介食物可以不試<br />\n之前有吹奏 六甲燒肉<br />\n啲食物好普通<br />\n重要係大陸留學生做待應"},{"pid":"c05b72fc773d78752e7ce30abfd1867bf70eef15","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"DAY 2 最後<br />\n我參考咗各方面意見，將心齋橋之類嘅行程放咗係夜晚<br />\n證明選擇正確，不過一般鋪頭8-9點都關門<br />\n藥妝就有部分開到好夜，半夜兩三點都有<br />\n所以想買藥妝真心唔急<br />\n一般時妝鋪頭雖然好早關，不過唔怕<br />\n個人認為唔需要係到行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDAY3<br />\n9點出發中之島漁港<br />\n11點幾出發海遊館<br />\n4點出發梅田行SHOPPING MALL<br />\n晚餐食CHISOZANMAI 自助餐<br />\n<br />\n個人認為呢日都幾改變我嘅步伐。<br />\n<br />\n係出發中之島前，買左海遊館one day pass先<br />\n好似2500/2300羊左右，抵過就咁買海遊館入場卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到阿波座落車，大約行十分鐘多少少會到<br />\n但去到附近以為自己去錯地方，因為鬼影都無隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當以為俾介紹條友老點之際<br />\n原來係有開檔！！！！！<br />\n不過得一檔野<br />\n<br />\n俾想像圖大家睇睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/202907_c5324329930d5063089f8ddfb279c2c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F202907_c5324329930d5063089f8ddfb279c2c6.jpg&h=101ffbea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/202908_ad30fd2f63f8b59cad7b95f9a60e6402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F202908_ad30fd2f63f8b59cad7b95f9a60e6402.jpg&h=91bceaf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/202910_2b7634e392e597c05f4f3519b3e632f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F202910_2b7634e392e597c05f4f3519b3e632f0.jpg&h=c7c0c32c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/202912_3f91fcd1580f3d909c36e06e801892db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F202912_3f91fcd1580f3d909c36e06e801892db.jpg&h=d2b7c816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對唔住，可能我地太早到<br />\n咩都沒有.........<br />\n<br />\n現實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/203137_3ded246ee08230d941a3ff6ce722b319.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F203137_3ded246ee08230d941a3ff6ce722b319.JPG&h=0a5f4abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/203140_c07772a8409209e726d40ffbb45ae986.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F203140_c07772a8409209e726d40ffbb45ae986.JPG&h=d77c4d1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/203143_fd29e182e3a23464b56958768b502531.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F203143_fd29e182e3a23464b56958768b502531.JPG&h=22caf04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/203144_0406f1b8e330adc53ea4e76b7835ac18.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F203144_0406f1b8e330adc53ea4e76b7835ac18.JPG&h=e32c042a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/203147_ae9890589f3a4fa9ff0666159087b34e.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F203147_ae9890589f3a4fa9ff0666159087b34e.JPG&h=93589ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/203148_182afe8e0520a1d73522220f7a961c26.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F203148_182afe8e0520a1d73522220f7a961c26.JPG&h=b7339fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/203150_69f0e2767edc1eebe5e0f90418f6cdf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F203150_69f0e2767edc1eebe5e0f90418f6cdf4.jpg&h=53495422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/203200_5b44005cab9cad11cc489ffbac07fcbb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F203200_5b44005cab9cad11cc489ffbac07fcbb.JPG&h=bb9b9898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/203202_eda5dcf46372970dd150d6e5f09c330d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F203202_eda5dcf46372970dd150d6e5f09c330d.JPG&h=710d0b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/203204_cde6d783d344c8492fe2b02546b4ed52.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F203204_cde6d783d344c8492fe2b02546b4ed52.JPG&h=f224b039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都有試到刺身，非一般鮮甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來俾貴價食咗屎先知道咩叫難得<br />\nbtw 我覺得暫時仲未超越到築地<br />\n可能試到燒物檔又唔同啲。<br />\n最後近12點嘅時候終於有少少人氣<br />\n有返幾個日本人嚟食野<br />\n亦見到幾個師傅準備<br />\n提議你地想去嘅話過咗中午先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我上網睇係話約6點會收檔，請預好時間<br />\n（當初仲為左中之島排開動物園行程，後來都食左屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"116db0181fabab7991d6b9bf26cbe78850b8ab29","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我下個星期日去，睇下有冇野抄考下先</blockquote><br />\n隨便，我都係係連登參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登推介食物可以不試<br />\n之前有吹奏 六甲燒肉<br />\n啲食物好普通<br />\n重要係大陸留學生做待應</blockquote><br />\n有時真係要自己伏過先知<br />\n我之前睇台灣blogger都係好伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada2e995d05b18d3b4d450c8d333624dcd9880f5","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:56:12.000Z","msg":"補圖<br />\n去中之島漁港途中<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/205535_c8810d1ef0c91a878933723a60ba6f73.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F205535_c8810d1ef0c91a878933723a60ba6f73.JPG&h=811d8486&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/205559_f5fb058a8c88cf0ffa6e26b546a31434.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F205559_f5fb058a8c88cf0ffa6e26b546a31434.JPG&h=c9053b9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b706a866ab0675f18cec07f3d34bfcb3e1613dcc","tid":475701,"uid":5324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"比個叻叻你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f399e37c4310f1b77fcc2f9992507ed2ddd20693","tid":475701,"uid":13837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T13:23:06.000Z","msg":"留名 <br />\n就快去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21385e