moji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台灣blog睇食物99.99%中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你有咩建議？你去瑞士係咩渠道睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日本就睇tabelog, 高分既<span style=\"color: red;\">通常</span>都唔會太伏<br />\n<br />\n歐洲睇trip advisor, 不過有時都伏伏地<br />\n瑞士既話我除左芝士火鍋個餐之外，其他都係行過見到覺得ok就食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留待下次再去做準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 謝謝"},{"pid":"6dfe3c5b43ae591cedacc983c13305e01140ad86","tid":475701,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"大阪燒肉我推介南森町 万両<br />\n呢間真係好好食，又唔貴<br />\n不過個到有兩間都叫万両，唔好去錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d790862f92bbd78a44b527b32cf0ddcc3ed4089d","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大阪燒肉我推介南森町 万両<br />\n呢間真係好好食，又唔貴<br />\n不過個到有兩間都叫万両，唔好去錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nRemark thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e84810207d749f3602cce1a4b5ceeccd22b9b5","tid":475701,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n隨便，我都係係連登參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登推介食物可以不試<br />\n之前有吹奏 六甲燒肉<br />\n啲食物好普通<br />\n重要係大陸留學生做待應</blockquote><br />\n有時真係要自己伏過先知<br />\n我之前睇台灣blogger都係好伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n台灣blog睇食物99.99%中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你有咩建議？你去瑞士係咩渠道睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得台灣blogger又末去到好伏<br />\n最多都係啲普通野佢地誇張左 未去到難食<br />\n同埋睇完佢地blog 自己睇埋ig location/tabelog就穩陣</blockquote><br />\n Tabelog唔識日文 淨係睇評分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIg location 好似好方便</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇評分ok ga la<br />\n3.0-3.3 唔洗去<br />\n3.3-3.6 可以經過食<br />\n3.6-3.9 值得搭1個鐘車程內去食<br />\n3.9-4.1  值得專登就佢booking時間黎度行程<br />\n4.1 up  值得專登係香港飛去食 7成book唔到位"},{"pid":"3fe2245c7a3ea8053cd02a884b6cb021a9caecc5","tid":475701,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大阪燒肉我推介南森町 万両<br />\n呢間真係好好食，又唔貴<br />\n不過個到有兩間都叫万両，唔好去錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nRemark thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nJapan, 〒530-0054 Ōsaka-fu, Ōsaka-shi, Kita-ku, Minamimorimachi, 1 Chome&minus;2&minus;14, 南森町ロイヤルハイツ<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/221928_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F221928_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=10fed107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb84ada42367c343b5a0e9a9f73f0a6c187cb46","tid":475701,"uid":36415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:25:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下如果shopping去邊到最好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想買啲日牌,earth, nice claup呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想去心齋橋呢啲咁多煌既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梅田會唔會好啲?</blockquote><br />\n天王寺q mall都有"},{"pid":"85a6d992c27117fd71c4422d5bf6ac11dfdde979","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:26:26.000Z","msg":"感謝兩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7180f4ba72e3eaab3f3a3553405836762870fa96","tid":475701,"uid":65142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下如果shopping去邊到最好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想買啲日牌,earth, nice claup呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想去心齋橋呢啲咁多煌既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梅田會唔會好啲?</blockquote><br />\n我最後個日有去outlet 好多日牌<br />\n不過你講nice claup我無留意<br />\n但真係好好行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後悔緊留太少時間<br />\nOutlet近機場叫rinku <br />\n<br />\n另外京都新京極都幾好<br />\n我聽日再打過 <br />\n早訓聽日開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲啲一月獨遊<br />\n睇下有咩參考先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c0aa7be596cca1dbf9a145db4563628ffce7bf","tid":475701,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"我想搵晚去中之島燒烤，個夜景幾靚"},{"pid":"65352631dfc23818c78c1a264157be806111efac","tid":475701,"uid":9411,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T16:18:05.000Z","msg":"扑左幾多次野？"},{"pid":"0acdb9497918594bcb639e333dd37da3dae94ae9","tid":475701,"uid":13138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T01:15:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我下個星期日去，睇下有冇野抄考下先</blockquote><br />\n隨便，我都係係連登參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n連登推介食物可以不試<br />\n之前有吹奏 六甲燒肉<br />\n啲食物好普通<br />\n重要係大陸留學生做待應</blockquote><br />\n下，依間好食喎"},{"pid":"79f4973a690ada1972d4e02cd9c0d19c90b5a72b","tid":475701,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T01:47:13.000Z","msg":"章魚燒真係超淋<br />\n好伏"},{"pid":"428ec37eb1ca61c71091ec8230ce28cad7814eaf","tid":475701,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T01:54:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d699bcdb479b6a1180c6aeb7f38b341972477563","tid":475701,"uid":90110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T04:42:01.000Z","msg":"想問下你酒店book左幾錢一晚？"},{"pid":"a0a17e55ac839e2cada1a0bcefc2a8da8abe4f82","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下你酒店book左幾錢一晚？</blockquote><br />\n平均$1000/晚"},{"pid":"620d4f17c2904820daec2a7774c3e3debc563214","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"由中之島漁港去海遊館要係大阪港落車<br />\n車程約半個鐘 落車行5-7分鐘<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/183802_beacda7f59115731ac5fdb9b98102c0a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F183802_beacda7f59115731ac5fdb9b98102c0a.JPG&h=2edef5c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入到去其實都唔會話好大期望，因為聽人講都係當海洋公園咁行<br />\n<br />\n但入到去真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n撞啱餵食秀，一玻璃之隔<br />\n仲要隻海獅衝過嚟都幾驚<br />\n呢個係入口位<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/184311_afaadefbed41387da66fcae134f91857.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F184311_afaadefbed41387da66fcae134f91857.JPG&h=cf9ede59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上去會睇吓水瀨先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/184640_eddaea4ebff7e597607da460c37cdf81.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F184640_eddaea4ebff7e597607da460c37cdf81.JPG&h=cb0623c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/184722_9003bb516c2e4820d57d4996a2e7103c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F184722_9003bb516c2e4820d57d4996a2e7103c.JPG&h=92dd4c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n始終動物唔郁唔活潑就好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但之後一上去就好興奮<br />\n其實我拍咗好多片好精彩 不過有我樣就唔出啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/185052_f24768c7bd2a1a9c2dd531a93eaadb5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F185052_f24768c7bd2a1a9c2dd531a93eaadb5b.JPG&h=beb003c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/185132_463135f921e1d436d09b35b17a0afe9f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F185132_463135f921e1d436d09b35b17a0afe9f.JPG&h=2af502f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/185209_effbe33bca2ecc55d9149c802c90ed44.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F185209_effbe33bca2ecc55d9149c802c90ed44.JPG&h=f16e83f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/185247_a30619039c9c0dfdef5774279b539fc8.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F185247_a30619039c9c0dfdef5774279b539fc8.JPG&h=63a06103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/185326_4093e8042d4c823ede0a8f50ff35c9f0.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F185326_4093e8042d4c823ede0a8f50ff35c9f0.JPG&h=bf4d1f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/185405_b2c2a76715d21c4c5e8ccaf93325d1a4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F185405_b2c2a76715d21c4c5e8ccaf93325d1a4.JPG&h=fcf00cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有片，有興趣可以睇吓<br />\n細路有啲嘈，睇嘅記住較細聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-tHPBfkLF2Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-tHPBfkLF2Q&d=5HpZ%2FrAUh5jvjgaTu3OudgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a411d456\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-tHPBfkLF2Q</a><br />\n仲有水豚君<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1KA9bUSQOhA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1KA9bUSQOhA&d=5HpZ%2FrAUh5jvjgaTu3OudgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=c8951583\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1KA9bUSQOhA</a><br />\n<br />\n最後仲去咗摸魔鬼魚同其他魚<br />\n我開心到好似細路咁，好低b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果鍾意動物又仲有少少童真嘅都啱你去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d5a4999086242815f52481f1e1c895bcffe3a2","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:15:23.000Z","msg":"原來兩段片都有聲，SORRY已DEL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800f7a16adc35df639027b5c2867a028560ddcb2","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"補返水豚君嘅相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/192134_803da03ced9482a743b5fac0c2b2b81a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F192134_803da03ced9482a743b5fac0c2b2b81a.JPG&h=afb9a758&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f46bf4e88df07653fe44c5148875305b3830421a","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:41:49.000Z","msg":"後來睇完海遊館嘅時候已經3點幾 <br />\n天都開始黑，當我諗住快啲走嘅時候<br />\n係天保山廣場對出空地有街頭藝人表演<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/192439_5b6cd006e2e25ffb09c24ed12eb32512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F192439_5b6cd006e2e25ffb09c24ed12eb32512.jpg&h=41e38f05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越晏天氣越寒，但睇咗一眼已經俾佢吸引住<br />\n優美嘅環境，人群因應街頭藝人嘅呼喚<br />\n由四散角落到慢慢圍觀席地而坐<br />\n係香港係較難遇到，通常吵鬧嘅環境已經令你想逃離人群<br />\n<br />\n望住一個認真嘅男人進行住會俾幾乎九成港女唾棄嘅表演<br />\n心入面有種感慨，可能好多人欣賞<br />\n但你會唔會俾自己另一半用好多時間去練習以上高難道表演<br />\n而唔係去上進同發奮？<br />\n<br />\n慢慢再睇，餘下嘅只有欣賞<br />\n令我嘅伐慢落嚟，亦令我呢個香港人知道咩叫生活<br />\n係個刻我先發現，我好似已經俾香港嘅生活吞噬咗<br />\n今日真正令我嘅旅程展開，適當嘅時候慢活同享受生活。"},{"pid":"fbe285a8519a87e2707db700f1ffd3026703ee7c","tid":475701,"uid":39745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想搵晚去中之島燒烤，個夜景幾靚</blockquote><br />\n夜景可以係京都睇，仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}